Source: https://github.com/vercel/next.js/blob/canary/docs/01-app/02-guides/migrating/app-router-migration.mdx

Fetch and cache data in the app directory using the fetch() API with default cache behavior (cache: 'force-cache'). This approach replaces getStaticProps functionality by automatically caching fetched data until manual invalidation, providing static site generation benefits.

